title: Rainbow Acres
description: Very well-stocked and comprehensive local health food market with a full service deli, hot foods bar, salad bar, and juice bar in the back of the store. Offers a wide range of natural products and natural food, grocery, specialty items. The in-house bakery makes all kinds of sweets and baked goods. Full service vitamins and supplements department; plus bulk staple, snack foods, fresh produce, frozen and refrigerated food, raw food, books, candles, yoga supplies, and much more. Also another location (smaller) in Marina Del Rey.
